msgid "A beheaded corpse."
msgstr "首を斬り落とされた死体。"

msgid "Saki's beheaded corpse lies here."
msgstr "首を斬られたサキの死体が転がっている。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_HOD_Death.chr_girl1.dlg.kat"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "That can't be..."
msgstr "そんな……そんなはずない……"

msgid "How is this possible?"
msgstr "こんなこと、ありえるわけがないでしょ？"

msgid "I just saw her a while ago..."
msgstr "少し前に会ったばかりなのに……"

msgid "I-I don't understand..."
msgstr "い、一体どうなってるの……"

msgid "A bloody corpse. The lower half is missing."
msgstr "血塗れの死体。下半身は無くなっている。"

msgid "Juli's bloody corpse. Her lower half is missing."
msgstr "ジュリの血塗れの死体。下半身は無くなっている。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_HOD_Death.chr_girl2.dlg.kat"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "I..."
msgstr "私の……"

msgid "This is my fault..."
msgstr "私のせいだ……"

msgid "A bloody corpse."
msgstr "血塗れの死体。"

msgid "Kaya's bloody corpse."
msgstr "カヤの血塗れの死体。"

msgid "Oh no no no no no..."
msgstr "嫌だ、嫌だ、嫌だ、嫌だ……"

msgid "Oh my god."
msgstr "そんなはずない……"

msgid "This can't be real... It's not real..."
msgstr "こんなの現実のはずない……これは現実じゃないのよ……"

msgid "Right...?"
msgstr "そうでしょ……？"

msgid "...The door..."
msgstr "……扉が……"

msgid "I can... leave...?"
msgstr "出られ……るの……？"

msgid "I can... go home...?"
msgstr "家に……帰れるの……？"

msgid "I don't want to die..."
msgstr "死にたくない……"

msgid "Why not? Everybody should try it at least once."
msgstr "どうして？　誰もが一度は経験するのに。"

msgid "Right."
msgstr "そうだ。"

msgid "...It doesn't light up..."
msgstr "……明るくならない……"

msgid "It's as if this place isn't dark... it's just black..."
msgstr "まるで暗いんじゃなく……ただ、真っ黒なだけみたい……"

msgid "That's not going to help."
msgstr "それは役に立たない。"

msgid "Unfortunately, the door has no keyhole."
msgstr "残念ながら、このドアには鍵穴はない。"

msgid "Blood."
msgstr "血だ。"

msgid "Blood puddles."
msgstr "血溜まりだ。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_HOD_Death.misc_blood_2.dlg.kat"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "There's no door here."
msgstr "ここにはドアはない。"

msgid "I cant... go back..."
msgstr "戻れ……ない……"

msgid "A welcoming door."
msgstr "歓迎するかのような扉。"

msgid "It's locked."
msgstr "鍵がかかっている。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_HOD_Death.move_exit.dlg.kat"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "I... have to..."
msgstr "ここから……"

msgid "...get out..."
msgstr "……出なきゃ……"
